Name: AccountCurrencyCode
Notes: The currency of the Customer account.

Name: AccountDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer account.

Name: AccountTimeZoneId
Notes: Name of the timezone of the Customer account. For example: "(GMT-05:00) Eastern Time".

Name: AdNetworkType1
Enum Values:
SEARCH / Search Network
CONTENT / Display Network
Notes:
First level network type.
Predicate values / display values:
SEARCH / Search Network
CONTENT / Display Network

Name: AdNetworkType2
Enum Values:
SEARCH / Google search
SEARCH_PARTNERS / Search partners
CONTENT / Display Network
Notes:
Second level network type (includes search partners).
Predicate values / display values:
SEARCH / Google search
SEARCH_PARTNERS / Search partners
CONTENT / Display Network

Name: AverageCpc
Notes: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

Name: AverageCpm
Notes: Average Cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM).

Name: AveragePosition
Notes: Your ad's position relative to those of other advertisers.

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignName
Notes: The name of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed
Notes:
The status of the Campaign.
Predicate values / display values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

Name: ConversionCategoryName
Notes: Not compatible with non-conversion stats (AverageCpc, Clicks, etc). Prevents zero-conversion rows from being returned.  Values: "Other", "View of a key page", "Purchase/Sale", "Signup", "Lead"

Name: ConversionRateManyPerClick
Notes: The number of conversions divided by total clicks that can be tracked to conversions. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionTypeName
Notes: Not compatible with non-conversion stats (AverageCpc, Clicks, etc).  Prevents zero-conversion rows from being returned.

Name: ConversionValue
Notes: The sum of conversion values for all conversions.

Name: ConversionsManyPerClick
Notes: This column reports total conversions, across all the conversion actions you're tracking. How you've chosen to count your conversions (unique or all) affects the number shown in this column.

Name: Cost
Notes: The sum of your cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM) costs during this period. Other costs such as cost-per-call aren't included. For a sum of all costs, use the TotalCost column.

Name: Ctr
Notes: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions). Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: CustomerDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer.

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

SUNDAY / Sunday
